reviewText: Enjoyed watching a professional in his element.  Capt. Clay handled his boat in a competent and relaxed manner.  The scenery was also awesome.

Every fisherman has tricks and techniques that work for him.  Clay has some tips that I had never quite perfected, e.g. filleting dolphin without gutting the fish. Good video that will be a handy reference for me and my kids for a long time to come.
